          <p>Last Updated: 10/09/2013 Build: 0.4v</p>
          <p>-Tested with wired Xbox360 Controllers</p>
          </br></br>
          <p>Xbox Controller:</p>
          <p>-Analog stick to move.  X to charge your kick, release to kick. A to dash. Right Bumper to Teleport</p>
          </br></br>
          <p>Keyboard:</p>
          <p>-Player One: WASD + V to charge your kick, release to kick. C to dash. F to Teleport.</p>
          <p>-Player Two: Arrows Keys + ' to charge your kick, release to kick. ; to dash. / to Teleport.</p>
          <p>Controls not optimized for keyboard. Sorry!</p>
